Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的命运究竟是否在由看不见的力量或法则来掌控？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像神之手吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  至少有一点很明确
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的自由不受任何意志的支配
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.28,0:00:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能加入我们  Guts！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺伤了我  又对我假施善心！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用剑来一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.63,0:00:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜欢用武力来解决问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.84,0:00:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何我都会得到自己想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了你的傲慢自大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.48,0:01:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让我恶心！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可不一般呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我敢说我用这把剑可以劈断钢铁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他却能轻易躲过了我的每次攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只用单手使用那把细剑！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真是个了不起的战士！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你愿意  我可以等你伤愈之后再战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会赢的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.12,0:03:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会击败你！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要再快点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再用点力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子真是不长记性  又在挑战Griffith了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Corkus  站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是Griffith的命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不许介入！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是个除掉他的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候轮到你发号施令了  Corkus？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许违抗Griffith的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抓到他了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欣赏你的战斗方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用各种手段来击败你的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我不动的话你也使不了剑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你这么僵持下去我也不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你唠唠叨叨的真是很烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战斗的时候，你的嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该像这样用！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没见过Griffith被打翻在地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的血味道如何呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打赌你那张漂亮的脸蛋从没挨过打！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他赢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确实打得我够呛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖的认输  否则我就会折断你的肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是我们的Griffith！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才像你  Griffith！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这手下败将！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来好可怜呀  是不是已经绝望了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是认真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在起他是鹰之团的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.16,0:06:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith从来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没对任何人说过这么亲切的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为鹰之团在战场上战无不胜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有了死神这样的绰号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不必担心他们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们都属于Midland军队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且  雇佣兵也没有火炮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  要是他们再这样下去并取得国王信任的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就会失去现在的地位  名誉和尊严的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是头疼呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:07:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全击败了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在做梦吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲起话来很亲切  而且笑起来像个纯真的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.41,0:08:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他却毫不犹豫地扭住我的肩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像在拆洋娃娃的胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要杀他吗  Corkus？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要前功尽弃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有7个人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也说过不喜欢他的  没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了  这个小鬼杀了Dan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  他太厉害了  而且精通剑术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了  就连Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会趁他不备时拿下他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  他现在受伤了也就拿不了剑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等把他的尸体抛进树林之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会让Griffith相信他是逃跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这群人可比不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:08:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sam  你先上！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从来不先上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.63,0:09:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们最好别这么干
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C-Caska
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就算受伤了，也还是比你们厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒要看个究竟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖的回到你们的帐篷里去  Corkus
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caska  为什么你要保护他？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和他睡了两个晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得你对他会有感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就砍掉你的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开-开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来我欠你两次人情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我应该谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是执行Griffith的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则  我才不会管你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我盼着你再打仗时赶紧死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那座山上  敌人的总部有2000名士兵把守
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的任务是要烧毁他们在后山的供应和其他一些补给品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:11:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般来讲  敌人都回重兵把守前山以防夜袭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的战术是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们沿河岸行军以便看起来像是在绕行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们要尝试从敌人背后发动奇袭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成任务之后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要取捷径而回  从敌军的正中央突围！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从敌人中央突破？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有后援吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.93,0:11:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说不会派遣部队来参加夜袭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都是一群胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后卫就由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guts
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你来担当
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要协助所有同伴逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时还要在丛林的小道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖住敌方数量众多的骑兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能胜任吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是命令  对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith想试试那孩子的本领
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的家伙  我估计他会死得很难堪的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没准会开溜的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith可不会用这样的重任来试探我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith真的很信任他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下我可不愁杀他了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们是在河中行军而不是按照预定的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实不管走哪条路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人也想不到我们会趟过急流发动奇袭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  这风声
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会压过我们行军的声响
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外  当我们从背面放火时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火势还可以借助风向扩散
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一步都尽在他的掌握之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么可怕的夜里还要放哨真是太糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我们  连狼也不会在这样的晚上出来活动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌-敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他他们怎么会从这个方向冲过来？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌-敌人来袭！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.45,0:14:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点火！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火药库着火了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别和他们玩了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一字形突围！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.15,0:14:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加快速度！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力脱出！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火势看起来要顺着风势蔓延到总部了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把重骑兵推前！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被几个雇佣兵攻破总部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对我们骑士来说简直是个奇耻大辱！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前可没见过这么高效率的突袭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  该看我的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我-我知道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  再快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打得好  Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一个月之内是不会轻举妄动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有些事情要办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢摆出这么无礼的态度！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的损失如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.57,0:16:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不值一提啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了我们的强力后卫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人根本就靠近不了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是在那样狭窄的林间小道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他自己就能应付一群骑兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真是有本领
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ricket！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guts在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他先让我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候返回了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我支持不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住我的手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放跑他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要回来？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别讲话！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会咬着舌头的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去可不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人太重了  会被抓住的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持住！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要穿过树林了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.34,0:18:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散开！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤-撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何  Guts的战斗方式真是令人吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如Griffith想的  他真是说到做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  哪儿也不见Guts的踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还很年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是Griffith有着出色的领导才能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身边的人也都完全相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外  他有着完美的判断力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道什么时候该采取什么行动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可不仅仅像是一个雇佣兵的头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guts先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这上边吹凉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你我才能及时逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Ricket
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.74,0:19:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好崇拜你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没见过除了Griffith以外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么出色的战士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只做了我该做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没什么值得好谢的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实  我不是来和你讨论这事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得跟我们来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚会缺了主角可不热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:20:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,底下正在开庆功会  也算是欢迎你的宴会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我-我可没让你们这么做啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你-你干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我下来，你个大头混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫Pippon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你-你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家听着！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们干杯来祝贺我们的新英雄！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被正式接纳了  新兵！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:20:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真叫人吃惊呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数量那么悬殊的情况下还能独自挡住敌人的进攻！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正像Griffith预料的  你真是说到做到呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你有点混，可是我更喜欢你跟我们在一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好乐乐吧  新兵！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.94,0:21:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.29,0:23:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人有时永远也无法获得解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.56,0:23:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寻求宽恕的过程中，个人的赎罪注定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要随着时光流逝而生活在痛苦之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是预示着未来的悲痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.90,0:23:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是隐藏在过去的悲痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一个才更痛苦？
